Ibrahim Sangaré (amụrụ n'ụbọchị nke abụọ n'ọnwa Disemba n'afọ 1997) bụ onye na-agba bọọlụ nke Ivorian nke na-agba ọsọ dị ka onye na-echebe etiti maka Eredivisie club PSV Eindhoven na ndị otu mba Ivory Coast.
Mgbe ọ malitere ọrụ ntorobịa ya na klọb ndị Ivorian Tout Puissant Koumassi na AS Denguélé, Sangaré malitere maka Toulouse na 0 0 0 010 tie na Angers na 22 Ọktoba 2016.
Na 28 Septemba 2020, Sangaré sonyeere PSV Eindhoven na nkwekọrịta afọ ise.
Sangaré nọchitere anya Ivory Coast U20 na 2015 Toulon Tournament, na Ivory Coast O23s na 2 friendly.
Akara na nsonaazụ depụtara ihe mgbaru ọsọ Ivory Coast nke mbụ.
